<div class="layout-cell layout-cell-12 data-cell"><a name='PP_A Geometria nos Livros Did&aacute;ticos de Matem&aacute;tica da Educa&ccedil;&atilde;o B&aacute;sica'></a><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-3 text-align-right">
